RUNTIME DOWNLOADS
-----------------
Users download additional software at runtime (bash, Python,
Node.js, etc.) from Termux package repositories. These are NOT
bundled with MobileCLI and are subject to their own licenses
(GPL, MIT, PSF, etc.).

TERMUX COMPATIBILITY
--------------------
MobileCLI uses the com.termux package name for compatibility
with the Termux terminal infrastructure. Termux is a trademark
of its respective owners. MobileCLI is an independent project.

